{"tid":1531240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！暴大開始多人！！","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T07:41:20.000Z","uid":299436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"baaabb441669fba618b5b3097664569c9e0403f8","tid":1531240,"uid":299436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"即時討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7640a6be452fe6deee66f95b04d2bf90185ce5ed","tid":1531240,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96b9280c0ab487e815a651744df568901bca035","tid":1531240,"uid":64153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"暴大要人呀！！！！"},{"pid":"8e292efd47ac6753a88c421be802af0889e8322a","tid":1531240,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbd08c0ff6914a9b55efe6281c481e97f9436be","tid":1531240,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之，攻其不備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>兵者詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"8ad911ab1627612743447be5be8f4330858398df","tid":1531240,"uid":299436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"pishhh"},{"pid":"00f82b7949e90e0433a80db6ffaf9c02ddf1dc2a","tid":1531240,"uid":299436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9c4f85e40a32572b8f59de96b0c96577bde2df2f","tid":1531240,"uid":80139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"暴大發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a70b13c5f4fec6b6a1a6876fe3d2fa1998d8b9d","tid":1531240,"uid":299436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2c24f7b736993cff5520665c1ffd6f521b410541","tid":1531240,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"相呢"},{"pid":"b685a78aad80e148281e9730e32924580fe1d87d","tid":1531240,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets